$RLF, $OCUP, $LLKKF

Ukraine --> Isolation of Russia --> Oil, Gas, etc spiking --> Stagflation fears --> Sell offs all over.

Sometimes doing the right thing has a price.

But it's not all doom : the right biotechs, or Lithium, Zinc, Nickel stocks, are holding or up.

Stay alert.
